t deforming the matter field. But the\npolar waves must perturb the energy density, the pressure and also the\nnon-azimuthal components of the fluid velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Jun 2021 18:25:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Sep 2021 18:31:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-15"}
