r the said spacetimes is an important consequence of the\npresence of the magnetic field. From the astrophysical point of view, our\nresult could be helpful to study the effects of (gravito)magnetic fields on the\npropagation of polarized photons in the strong gravity regime of the collapsed\nobject.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2021 11:21:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Aug 2021 17:04:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2022 16:48:48 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2022 16:31:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-01"}
