\nmetrics: the number of iterations, the total amount of bits communicated, and\nwall-clock time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2021 11:30:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 22:13:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-14"}
