artly eliminated by considering the cortical bone in\nthe 3C-MR attenuation map. Hypo-perfusion was perceived in Frontal and Temporal\nlobes in SPECT-MRAC images of the anosmic group.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2021 15:22:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-08"}
